      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c269719217868ea32b0a3aa"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "I've done a search on the <i>Argo</i>'s records and whatever sources I can find and there is no reference to the term she used right before dying.\n\nPlus I am not even sure of how it's spelled, 'ilKee', ilKhi' or whatever it is, likely some pirate lingo that only the Kittens understood.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "So the 'IlChi' is just a dead end?",
