      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ca9a2e01b8fa025d357647a"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "We have already suffered enough after years of war.\n\nMy uncle justified the Directorate and his coup to defend the Reach from the envy and greed of foreign powers.",
